content: **Ahoy Sailors, here are the the last few weeks of changes. 10/12 - 10/23

fields.name: Spooktober updates
fields.value:
- We are pleased to have released our Halloween themed lobby and content for this season. Hope you are enjoying the new view!
- Next week we have a special surprise  coming out so watch for updates towards the end of the week.

fields.name: New Kim Features
fields.value:
- Flip a coin "Flip a coin"
- Rock paper scissors "Lets play rock paper scissors"
- Learn what server you are on "What server am I on / what server is this"
- Working on better and smarter responses. 
- Less generalized responses

fields.name: Chest dupe fix
fields.value: - Removed the ability to duplicate items using the chest breaking method

fields.name: Bedwars
fields.value: - Fixed blue bed in bedwars desert map.
